# <type>(<scope>): <subject>   ← 50 chars max, imperative mood
#
# <body>  ← wrap at 72 chars. Explain *what* and *why*, not *how*.
#
# <footer>  ← e.g. "Closes #123", "BREAKING CHANGE: ..."
#
# Conventional Commit types:
#   feat     new feature            fix      bug fix
#   docs     documentation          style    formatting (no code change)
#   refactor code change, no fix/feat        perf   performance
#   test     tests                  build    build system / deps
#   ci       CI config              chore    misc / tooling
#   revert   revert a previous commit
